 (e.g., for PBE functional under pressure):INCAR (Input Parameters):

SYSTEM = Lonsdaleite DFT Optimization
ENCUT = 500          # Plane-wave cutoff (eV)
ISMEAR = 0; SIGMA = 0.05  # Gaussian smearing
GGA = PE             # PBE functional
IBRION = 2           # Geometry optimization
ISIF = 3             # Relax cell + ions
NSW = 100            # Max ionic steps
EDIFF = 1E-6         # Energy convergence
EDIFFG = -0.01       # Force convergence (eV/Å)
PSTRESS = 25         # Apply 25 GPa pressure

