Raman Spectra Simulation: Phonon density of states; lonsdaleite peak at 1,330 cm⁻¹ (shifted 2 cm⁻¹ from cubic 1,332 cm⁻¹). Includes pressure dependence (up to 50 GPa).
Scientific Reports (NV in lonsdaleite, 2025) 
